data.description: SPACIOUS END-UNIT RANCH WITH PRIVATE PATIO & COURTYARD STYLE ENTRANCE! Welcome to this tucked away subdivision offering a truly story-book feel! As you enter this stunning home note the beautiful brick curb appeal, end-unit location, ample guest parking, & spacious attached garage! Upon entrance, take note of the stunning hardwood floors, fresh neutral paint, sunny south/west facing exposures & ample foyer closet space! Entertain with ease in the spacious family room offering a gorgeous double-sided fireplace! The eat-in-kitchen features a dining area with cozy fireplace views, ample cabinetry space, custom cabinet drawers perfect for keeping organized, a new commercial-grade vent hood, & breakfast bar! Host events effortlessly with access to your private patio just off of the kitchen! Enjoy summer grilling or winter coca while enjoying views of mature trees and no neighbors behind you! Retreat to the expansive primary bedroom featuring a private en-suite, enormous closet space, upgraded bamboo flooring, & a airy ceiling height! The primary bedroom en-suite features a spacious shower, separate soaking tub, & upgraded double sink vanity! Convenient main floor laundry is located just off of the kitchen and boasts upgraded washer/dryer! Guests will enjoy their own spacious bedroom and bathroom! The enormous basement boasts tall ceilings making it ideal for additional living space, a rec room, gym, or for additional storage! Enjoy the RARELY AVAILABLE WHEEL-CHAIR FRIENDLY garage ramp, easy front door access, and bathroom grab bars! Take advantage of your free time! The well run HOA will maintain your lawn and keep on top of snow removal! Enjoy a tranquil community which feels hidden away but is near to shopping, restaurants, entertainment, parks, & trails! Quick access to Metra & highways! Low HOA, affordable taxes, move-in-ready, & meticulously maintained. This is the one you've been waiting for!
